<HEADLINE>
A FEDERAL CASE: PILING IT ON TO THE G-MEN 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(ART ADV: Graphic is being sent to NYT graphic clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling (888)
603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
(bl) 
 By STEVEN A. HOLMES   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ There was a time when G-men wore fedoras and hunted
down bank robbers, kidnappers and spies. Now, in addition to all
that, federal law-enforcement agents are being asked to track down
