<SLUG> BC-CYBERSCENE23-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    For silly info, try these sites
 &HT;    By Bill Husted
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
