<SLUG> BC-MAC-REPORT23-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    New three-screen format makes MacInTax program easier to figure
 &HT;    By Charles Haddad
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   You know it must be tax time when Intuit releases its latest
version of MacInTax.
</P>
<P>
   This year's update is a keeper. Intuit has made great strides in
improving MacInTax's ease of use. The program is both easier to
navigate and configure.
</P>
