</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LEBANON-BAALBEK-$ADV27-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    LAVISH STONE CARVINGS AND MONUMENTAL TEMPLES MAKE BAALBEK
SPECTACULAR
 &HT;    With Photos.
 &HT;    With LEBANON-NIGHTLIFE-$ADV27; LEBANON-BOX-$ADV27.
