<SLUG> BC-MICROSOFT23-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    JUDGE TO TAKE MICROSOFT TRIAL OFF THE STAND
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
